item.title: Help error_game_js5connect
item.dc:creator: @Yz85Racer Yz85Racer
item.description:
@Yz85Racer wrote:

Upon inititial connection, the client will send you a single byte ‘15’. If it is 15, the client is requesting the update server, which (the update server) will be responsibile to send the client the update keys, which in this case is:
